**/CLAUDE.local.md
**/.claude-shared.md
**/.claude-fragments/

# Real bank statements (PII) — never commit; finance-csv fixtures must be anonymized
extratos/

# Secrets
*.keys.json
.env
.env*

# Temp files
.tmp-*

# OS
.DS_Store

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/

# Skills system (local per-installation state)
.nanoclaw/

agents-sdk-docs

# Python bytecode (watch skill scripts)
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# watch skill: session cookies (secret — never commit)
.watch-cookies.txt
